So, Boris,
I am going to finish very soon,

00:21:58.580 --> 00:22:03.224
because we arrived to
the axis of the axis (Sushumna Nadi)

00:22:03.425 --> 00:22:05.302
and here it is, the sthiti.

00:22:05.503 --> 00:22:10.560
You know, Shri Mataji teased us
and told us to count how many people

00:22:10.761 --> 00:22:15.466
we gave realisation. But believe me,
I never counted in my entire life,

00:22:15.667 --> 00:22:18.091
how many people
I gave realisation to,

00:22:22.073 --> 00:22:26.104
But if we get ourselves
in the sthiti state,

00:22:26.620 --> 00:22:32.161
then just our being there
will raise Kundalinis.

00:22:44.503 --> 00:22:47.357
So the journey for us
is towards the Stithi,

00:22:47.558 --> 00:22:52.318
because these are where then
we are going to get

00:22:52.519 --> 00:22:59.253
the blessings of Shri Shiva

00:22:59.472 --> 00:23:01.588
which is Kalyan.

00:23:02.409 --> 00:23:05.255
Kalyan, there is a speech
of Shri Mataji on this,

00:23:05.456 --> 00:23:06.513
maybe you can hear it.

00:23:06.714 --> 00:23:10.620
But Kalyan is the state where we are
blessed on all sides.

00:23:24.162 --> 00:23:26.297
If we can all understand

00:23:26.498 --> 00:23:33.375
that our most important job
is to be what we claim to be

00:23:33.724 --> 00:23:35.344
- the job is done.

00:23:35.545 --> 00:23:38.271
And I am very confident

00:23:38.623 --> 00:23:43.875
that we are all together
on the right path.

00:23:44.599 --> 00:23:49.491
You see, there is a relationship
between (seeking and finding)

00:23:49.692 --> 00:23:53.320
because seekers are
in the evolution bowl

00:23:53.521 --> 00:23:56.984
and yogis are not
in the evolution bowl.

00:23:57.185 --> 00:24:00.049
But there is a relationship
between the two.

00:24:01.386 --> 00:24:06.065
The link is in the name
of Shri Lakshmi,

00:24:09.680 --> 00:24:11.377
Anantasta.

00:24:11.578 --> 00:24:14.530
Because Shri Lakshmi
is the power of evolution

00:24:14.731 --> 00:24:16.994
She is the Shakti of Shri Vishnu,
She becomes Mahalakshmi,

00:24:17.195 --> 00:24:20.534
She is the power of evolution.
Mahalakshmi is the power of evolution.

00:24:20.735 --> 00:24:24.778
There is a name Shri Lakshmi, where
She is said to be Anantasta,

00:24:24.979 --> 00:24:27.992
which means She resides in eternity.

00:24:28.532 --> 00:24:31.844
So, eternity
is the eternal present,

00:24:32.672 --> 00:24:37.625
eternity is when we are
in Nirvichara Samadhi,

00:24:37.857 --> 00:24:40.107
eternity is peaceful.

00:24:40.638 --> 00:24:45.966
So, before we were evolving
through action-reaction,

00:24:46.167 --> 00:24:48.594
synthesis, disorder,

00:24:48.795 --> 00:24:50.255
petitions,

00:24:50.638 --> 00:24:54.922
letters on the e-mail,
accusing, descending

00:24:55.123 --> 00:24:57.123
- that was before.

00:24:57.442 --> 00:25:01.531
Most yogis have the intelligence
to understand

00:25:01.732 --> 00:25:03.732
that this is not our model,

00:25:03.933 --> 00:25:10.042
most yogis understand that
evolution now for us is peaceful.

00:25:11.579 --> 00:25:15.500
We don't need to do anything
- we become.

00:25:16.610 --> 00:25:19.917
This is what Sahaj is.

00:25:20.766 --> 00:25:25.026
You will see temptations
to make out of Sahaj a cult,

00:25:25.227 --> 00:25:29.937
to make out of Sahaj a sect,
to make out of Sahaj a religion.

00:25:30.844 --> 00:25:35.018
Shri Mataji
through the 10 years of withdrawal

00:25:35.219 --> 00:25:40.667
has allowed those options
to develop in small doses,

00:25:41.211 --> 00:25:46.216
but this is processed by the collective
the consciousness of the yogis

00:25:46.417 --> 00:25:48.417
who are in Sahaja sthiti.

00:25:48.711 --> 00:25:53.135
So, you see, if we are as a collective,
we go to the Sahaj sthiti,

00:25:53.336 --> 00:25:55.674
which is the only direction
where we want to go,

00:25:55.875 --> 00:25:58.549
which is the reason
why you came to Sahaja Yoga.

00:25:58.750 --> 00:26:01.237
We didn't come to Sahaja yoga...

00:26:01.438 --> 00:26:04.758
You came to Sahaja Yoga
to be Sat-Chitt-Ananda.

00:26:05.024 --> 00:26:07.659
And we all understand that we are all
brothers and sisters

00:26:07.860 --> 00:26:10.797
we all want that
- there is no animosity,

00:26:11.172 --> 00:26:12.969
there is no fight,

00:26:13.180 --> 00:26:15.917
there is forgiveness,
there is compassion

00:26:16.118 --> 00:26:19.833
but there is also the courage
to stand by the Truth,

00:26:21.657 --> 00:26:24.359
because the Truth is this
(the axis).

00:26:25.414 --> 00:26:28.807
If yogis don't have the courage
to stand by the Truth,

00:26:29.008 --> 00:26:30.906
they miss the axis,

00:26:31.157 --> 00:26:34.070
and my sense is that in

00:26:34.875 --> 00:26:38.234
the collective overall there is,

00:26:38.435 --> 00:26:41.245
(even if they cannot explain it
in a speech like this),

00:26:41.446 --> 00:26:45.016
but there is an understanding
that this is what they want.

00:26:45.217 --> 00:26:48.430
And this is the reason
why there is progress in Sahaja Yoga,

00:26:48.631 --> 00:26:50.893
although you don't think so,
because you see division,

00:26:51.094 --> 00:26:58.271
you see fighting, you see various
things, but actually we are growing.

00:26:58.472 --> 00:27:02.776
There is more awareness,
there is more understanding.

00:27:03.151 --> 00:27:08.161
For instance, when we came here,
yesterday we arrived at this hotel

00:27:08.362 --> 00:27:11.802
you know,
this did not happen like that,

00:27:12.003 --> 00:27:17.375
when I was going to seminars
in Austria 25 years ago

00:27:17.667 --> 00:27:20.721
- you know, I arrived at the hotel,
I became thoughtless.

00:27:20.922 --> 00:27:22.482
Why did I become thoughtless?

00:27:22.683 --> 00:27:26.169
Not because of the hotel, but otherwise
I would give him one more star.

00:27:26.370 --> 00:27:28.943
I became thoughtless
because all of you

00:27:29.144 --> 00:27:32.247
at that moment were coming,
driving towards this hotel

00:27:32.448 --> 00:27:35.924
with the desire to be
all together for this weekend.

00:27:38.268 --> 00:27:40.956
So let's have faith in ourselves.
